strings: <Cap><leader> discovers a new recipe for the alchemy pot!
<se_def>*: That elysium bird over there can't resist anything shiny.
<se_def>*: She buries everything she collects in the sand.
<se_low>*: A human used to live here before. A human so pure and good that even we monsters took a shine to him.
<se_low>*: You're the first <IF_SOLO>human<ELSE_NOT_SOLO>humans<ENDIF_SOLO> I've seen here since his death.
